bug.description: Despite being written as a docstring in the code, the method appears to be missing from the API docs. A <denchmark-link:https://apple.github.io/turicreate/docs/api/search.html?q=annotate&check_keywords=yes&area=default>search of the site</denchmark-link> shows no results for annotate, and the <denchmark-link:https://apple.github.io/turicreate/docs/api/turicreate.toolkits.image_classifier.html>image classifier namespace</denchmark-link> shows only the method and the type.
